  "body": "Harmony Blockchain has used modified geth but it does not include \"totalDifficulty\" in its RPC response. I think that Hardhat should support the option to omit this field for better supporting alternative chains.\r\n\r\n```\r\n# Step1\r\nnpx hardhat node --fork https://a.api.s0.t.hmny.io/\r\n\r\n# Step2: call some methods\r\n\r\n\r\nInvalid JSON-RPC response's result.\r\n  \r\nErrors: Invalid value undefined supplied to : RpcBlockWithTransactions | null/totalDifficulty: QUANTITY\r\n```",
